                1.	Tax computation, planning and management<br />
                2.	Computation of advance tax and TDS Compliances<br />
                3.	Tax compliance reporting<br />
                4.	Inbound and outbound tax advisory and support services<br />
                5.	Withholding Tax<br />
                6.	Advising on tax planning and tax management, availing tax concessions, incentives, reliefs and tax benefits<br />
                7.	Transfer pricing services<br />
            </p>

        </div>

    </div>
